The paper discusses Transfer Learning (TL) methods for classification problems, which are commonly studied in the fields of machine learning, artificial intelligence, computer vision, natural language processing, and software engineering. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
